Onboard Loan Applicants Faster with Guided Application Intake

Eliminate the inefficiencies with the tedious loan origination process by offering your agents or relationship managers a guided application intake experience. With guided application intake, reduce the need for applicants to visit banks for physical verification or for providing documents. Agents can complete the loan application forms with more accuracy and minimal manual effort. Your loan officers or mid-office agents can efficiently verify applicant and application details, and collect additional details to ensure underwriters have the required information to decide application eligibility.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions where Digital Lending—India is enabled.

When: Digital Lending—India is available starting on July 16, 2024.
title: Streamline Loan Origination with Guided Application Intake
